"{\"uid\": \"tribune.com.pk-story-2484184-olympic-surfer-gabriel-medinas-record-setting-ride-caught-in-viral-photo\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"US  The viral photo captures Olympic surfer Medina in a perfect moment of triumph.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 82, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 2, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9862235305705973, \"rank\": 0.013342583008994536, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 44, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.036676156829448e-16, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics have produced numerous memorable moments, but none have captured the public's imagination quite like a photo of Gabriel Medina's mid-air celebration during the surfing event in Tahiti.\", \"from\": 84, \"to\": 287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 88, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 215, \"end\": 229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Medina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999995556305371, \"rank\": 4.419489418570985e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photographer Jerome Brouillet, working for Agence France-Presse, captured the Brazilian surfer in a striking pose as he performed a celebratory gesture after a record-setting ride.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerome\", \"score\": 0.9999999998342446, \"rank\": 1.4702535971343265e-10, \"text\": \"Jerome\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerome\"}, {\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}, {\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Agence France-Presse\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The image shows Medina and his board appearing to levitate above the waves, with Medina's raised index finger signalling his triumph.\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.036676156829448e-16, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.036676156829448e-16, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by SportsCenter (@sportscenter)  The 30-year-old Medina, a three-time World Surf League champion, secured a near-perfect score of 9.90, setting a new Olympic record for a single wave run.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SportsCenter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SportsCenter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SportsCenter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SportsCenter\"}, {\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.036676156829448e-16, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999843112, \"rank\": 1.5636044178947447e-11, \"text\": \"World Surf League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His triumphant kick-out from the wave, anticipated by Brouillet, added to the photo's dramatic impact.\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brouillet\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brouillet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brouillet, who has been photographing surfing for nearly a decade, expressed his surprise at the photo's viral success.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never thought it was possible that this shot would be so much appreciated, but I can understand why,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The photo quickly gained traction online, amassing countless reshares and praise.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Medina's outstanding performance propelled him to a total score of 17.40, moving him into the quarterfinals against compatriot Joao Chianca.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.036676156829448e-16, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medina's impressive ride came during optimal conditions at Teahupo'o, with waves described as \\\"serious\\\" before weather conditions forced a postponement of the women's competition.\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.036676156829448e-16, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"COMMENTS  Comments are moderated and generally will be posted if they are on-topic and not abusive.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, please see ourComments FAQ  This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten,                     redistributed or derived from.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unless otherwise stated, all content is                     copyrighted \\u00a9 2025 The Express Tribune.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": []}]}"